for many years I have been driving the same roads and suddenly the speed limit has been reduce to 20mph where is clearly not needed. areas like Streatham common vale. Cristal palace parade ( A212 ) 
Council didn't run a survey to consult the public about the road changes or disclose information with real facts about why they needed to change the speed from 30mph to 20mph. 
also it is a real harm to the environment with cars producing more CO2 having the engine running for longer periods
